Dubai
My client is seeking a demand planner to plan future sales and demands for the business they will also be responsible for managing the current overall stock position with a view to minimize any overstock and maximize sales.
You must have at least 5 years’ experience in a senior planning position in main high street fashion chain or large household retail chain.Sound knowledge around retail planning, distribution, merchandise financial budgeting and assortment planning.
Must have 4-5 years’ experience of stock management and sales forecasting system knowledge of SAP preferred.
This is a fantastic opportunity to work for a very successful international business with great benefits and the chance to earn great tax free salary
Salary TAX FREE up to £50k plus generous relocation benefits
